<sect1 id="dir_b5d4d16eb8a35bef91bda898d9a12dca_1autotoc_md608">
<title>helios::engine::runtime::spawn::policy::conditions</title><para>Spawn conditions for controlling spawn timing.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_b5d4d16eb8a35bef91bda898d9a12dca_1autotoc_md609">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides SpawnCondition implementations that determine when spawning should occur based on time, triggers, or other game state.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_b5d4d16eb8a35bef91bda898d9a12dca_1autotoc_md610">
