<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>condition<sp/>=<sp/>std::make_unique&lt;TimerSpawnCondition&gt;(2.0f);</highlight></codeline>
